"title": "8614: prayer, answers to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8614: prayer, answers to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God has promised to answer prayer for personal or corporate needs and for the needs of others.</p>\n<h2>God answers the prayers of individuals</h2>\n<h3>God answers the psalmists' prayers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:18-Ps145:19\">PSA 145:18–145:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:4\">PSA 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:8-Ps6:9\">PSA 6:8–6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:2-Ps30:3\">PSA 30:2–30:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:19-Ps66:20\">PSA 66:19–66:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1-Ps116:2\">PSA 116:1–116:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:5\">PSA 118:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:3\">PSA 138:3</a></p>\n<h3>God answers Moses' prayers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:23-Exod15:25\">EXO 15:23–15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:4-Exod17:7\">EXO 17:4–17:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:10-Num11:17\">NUM 11:10–11:17</a></p>\n<h3>God answers Hannah's prayer for a son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:27\">1SA 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:10-1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:10–1:20</a></p>\n<h3>God answers the prayers of the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:6\">PSA 99:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:9\">1SA 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:55-Lam3:57\">LAM 3:55–3:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:1-Jonah2:2\">JON 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:17–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>God answers the prayers of the kings of Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3\">1KI 9:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:31\">2CH 18:31</a></p>\n<h2>God answers corporate petition</h2>\n<h3>Answered prayer for deliverance from hardship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:7-Deut26:8\">DEU 26:7–26:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:23-Exod2:25\">EXO 2:23–2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7-Exod3:9\">EXO 3:7–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:16\">NUM 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:8\">1SA 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:7\">PSA 81:7</a></p>\n<h3>Answered prayer for deliverance from enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:10-1Sam12:11\">1SA 12:10–12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:9\">JDG 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:15\">JDG 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:19-2Kgs19:20\">2KI 19:19–19:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:20\">1CH 5:20</a></p>\n<h2>God answers the prayer of the oppressed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22-Exod22:23\">EXO 22:22–22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:28\">JOB 34:28</a></p>\n<h2>God answers prayer for healing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14-Jas5:16\">JAS 5:14–5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10-Num12:15\">NUM 12:10–12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:21-1Kgs17:22\">1KI 17:21–17:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:35\">2KI 4:32–4:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1-2Kgs20:6\">2KI 20:1–20:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24\">2CH 32:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1-Isa38:6\">ISA 38:1–38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:3\">MAT 8:2–8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:40-Mark1:42\">MRK 1:40–1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:12-Luke5:13\">LUK 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:40\">ACT 9:40</a></p>\n<h2>God answers prayer for others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:18-Deut9:19\">DEU 9:18–9:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:8-1Sam7:9\">1SA 7:8–7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5-Acts12:8\">ACT 12:5–12:8</a></p>",
